Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.72,0:00:02.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guilt all gone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:07.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:09.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,One more! One more!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:12.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Kushieda-senpai \Nacting a little strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:13.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:19.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always been odd, but she {\i1}has{\i0}\Nbeen spacing out a lot recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:39.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What am I doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:44.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,(My Silky Love)\NEvery time I think of you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:44.02,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,MY SILKY LOVE nijuu yojikan zutto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:47.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,(My Silky Love)\Nfor 24 hours straight,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:47.52,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,MY SILKY LOVE kimino koto omoutabi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:51.11,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,(My Silky Love)\NIt only makes me feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:51.11,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,MY SILKY LOVE modokashii kono kimochi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:55.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,(My Silky Love)\Nthat much more impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:55.03,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,MY SILKY LOVE tada afure kaetteku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:01:01.99,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so simple just to say I love you.\NBut when you come close to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:01:01.99,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,sukito ieba kantan nanoni\Nkimiga maeni kichauto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:08.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,my own emotions go awry\Nand get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:08.96,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kyaraga sobie watashino\Nkoto wo jamashiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:16.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I can bring myself to do anything.\NThat's who I'm supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:16.63,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,itsumonaraba tsuyoki de ikeru\Nsonna seikakunanoni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:22.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But I just can't break this\Nwall down no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:22.85,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,donna ganbatte mitemo kabewa kuzusenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:26.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Please understand these feelings for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:26.44,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,sasshite hoshii kono kimoch iwo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:29.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why these gazes of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:29.94,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,dakara watashi wa itsumo kimini
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:33.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,they tell my love for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:33.57,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,daisuki dayoto okuru shisen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.57,0:01:37.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Now gather up my courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.57,0:01:37.61,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,saidaino yuukide
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:41.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A fragile heart made of silk,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:41.16,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,yabure souna shirukuno haato
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:44.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that by meeting you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:44.66,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kimini atte kizuita yatto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:50.38,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so clumsy when it comes to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:50.38,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,ainiwa bukiyou dattan datte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:55.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A forgotten scar left in my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:55.13,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,wasure kaketa koino kizuato
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:58.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,and I suddenly felt it sting deep inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:58.76,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kyuuni uzuki dashitano kyunto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:03.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say that I love you someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:03.14,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,itsukawa watashi rashiku sukito iwanakya
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:08.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Or it'll keep making me weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:08.02,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,imayori yowaku nacchauyo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:15.53,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Mercury is Retrograde at Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:18.95,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the big year-end sales\Nare coming up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:20.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And then it's spring cleaning time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:23.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be free to scrub those typically\Nhard-to-reach places,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:26.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,like the backs of cupboards\Nand under tatami mats...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:28.54,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:31.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be thinking about\NChristmas! Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:34.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:35.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to be a good \Ngirl for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:39.38,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably approaching\NJapanese airspace about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:40.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't that be obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:44.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa! As in, Santa Claus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:47.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Gimme that! I'll carry it for you.\N- I looooove Santa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:49.27,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Are you...okay?\N- Do you, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:50.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:51.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope he comes to our\Nhouse again this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:52.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Uh-huh!\N- What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:59.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I love Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:01.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I gathered that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:03.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But my question is, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:05.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I need a reason to love Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole town is all pretty and sparkling...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:09.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's all smiles...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no eating sweets before dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:14.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:15.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm only having one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you {\i1}don't{\i0} know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:19.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We're celebrating the end of\Nyour suspension tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:22.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm using wild-caught\Namberjack for the hot pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, it was expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:25.51,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You could at least feign excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:27.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, yahoo, amberjack hot pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:28.43,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:30.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of amberjack, yipeekiyay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:31.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Not quite there yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:32.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:38.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get any closer to Minorin\Nwhile I was suspended?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:41.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No progress, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:42.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:46.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to waste the perfect chance,\Nsince I wasn't around to bug you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:49.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But it really wasn't my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:53.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,While you were gone, Kushieda didn't\Ncome to our usual meeting spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:55.42,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,and she ate lunch with some other girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:57.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus she's busy with practice after school—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:04:00.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So what, you gonna wait\Nforever, like Hachiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:05.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Think if you wait passively long enough,\Nshe'll make the first move?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:07.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid, idiotic, blockheaded mongrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:09.89,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Or that's what I'd normally say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:11.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:14.81,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can't blame you\Nfor making no progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:15.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:17.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.11,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:24.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The lovely angel of romance,\NTaiga, will lend you her aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Cr-Creepy as hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But I am a living Buddha right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:32.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A Buddha? Aren't you supposed\Nto be an angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:34.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:39.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovely angel Taiga is willing\Nto shed a layer or two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:43.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,or even go buck naked in order to\Nbring everyone a happy Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:44.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:47.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:48.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't I look like an angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:51.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:53.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're dropping crumbs on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:53.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:55.81,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Brush them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:58.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:04:59.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Lady Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:00.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tiger has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:04.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tiger, we appreciate your service!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:06.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:11.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We became fans of Lady Tiger\Nafter watching her fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:14.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The Boss vs. Palm-top Tiger showdown\Nended in victory for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:17.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you learned that The Boss\Nwas going to study abroad,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:20.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,you wanted to settle things\Nonce and for all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:20.88,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us about the fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:23.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:26.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a very difficult battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I faced peril many times!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:28.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:31.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The last person standing, wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:31.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:35.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the true victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:40.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, just ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:41.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:47.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Tensed up thighs!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:52.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Quivering muscles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:53.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:55.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:57.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:59.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So stop singing weird songs,\Nand give me a hug!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:03.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Release me! I am a human being!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:06.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed you so, so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:10.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why weren't you at our usual meeting spot!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:14.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I overslept, so I had to dash to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:16.43,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,My thighs are all banged up now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:20.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But how did I get to class\Nbefore you, if I was late?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:21.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:22.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:26.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We were surrounded by a bunch of weirdos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:27.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, Kushieda—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:29.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence, child!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd I just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.45,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I make a bad joke!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:37.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I've done it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:39.42,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yowzers! Sorry! Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,'Sup, Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:44.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and Tiger. Been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:46.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Doing good?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:47.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:49.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda snap again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:52.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I should shave my head for real...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:54.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What a failure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:57.43,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sporting the bald look for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:07:03.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, why is a girl in high school\Nwearing a bald cap?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:06.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:11.99,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:13.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Aisaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:15.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, Ki-Ki-Kitamura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:16.95,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- And good morning to you too, Takasu.\N- G-Good morning...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:18.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:22.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that! Your pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:24.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:26.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...the ultimate form of prostration!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:27.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Pro—?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:29.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Prostration!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:33.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting on my knees would be insufficient\Nto express my gratitude to Aisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So I went with full prostration!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:38.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:39.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:43.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Never get in another fight,\Nno matter who it's for!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:49.28,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're ever facing an insurmountable\Nchallenge, come talk to me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:52.99,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:08:00.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- {\i1}But then, I saw him.{\i0}\N- {\i1}Right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:04.08,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That teacher's assistant, walking\Nout of a pachinko parlor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:06.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, that would confirm it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He said he was late for \Nyour date because of work,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:10.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,but he was actually gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:11.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:13.05,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Broadcasting Room
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:13.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:15.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I texted one of my girl friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:20.35,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,My TA boyfriend is being\Nabsolutely horrible to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:21.81,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:23.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:25.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned something incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A thrilling turn of events?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:30.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The teacher's assistant position\Nno longer exists.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:33.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're called junior professors now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which would mean...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:37.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,He was lying about his job!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:40.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I haven't heard from him since!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:49.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you making our\Nteacher cry, Kitamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:52.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We should pretend we don't know it was her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:54.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yeah...\N- {\i1}Oh, well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:56.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This was Kitamura Yusaku, Patron \NSaint of Broken Hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:58.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with Cheering Your Love On.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:09:01.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this Patron Saint\Nof Broken Hearts thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:06.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, after his big confession,\NKitamura's become a romance guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:11.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Or at least, worshipped by people\Nlooking to do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:15.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura shoulders all their baggage,\Nand that somehow makes him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:18.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,the lucky patron saint of broken hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.95,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids in this school really love\Nto believe in legends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:28.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this broadcast annoying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:31.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he talking about studying for exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.51,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't the title of this show\NCheering Your Love On?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:35.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:37.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiger's listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:40.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't be able to hear Kitamura's\Nprofound broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:41.89,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tiger, you good?\NHearing everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:44.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:45.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:49.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, you seem awful quiet today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:52.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Desks and chairs would normally\Nbe flying by this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:54.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And Haruta would be a dead man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:58.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I'm being a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:09:59.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Good girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:03.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. I'm going to be a good\Ngirl for Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:06.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Santa is watching us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:09.38,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:12.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected "Santa" to ever\Ncome out of your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:13.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so not you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:15.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Dumb-chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:20.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa won't visit your\Nhouse if you're naughty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:23.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's definitely wrong with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:25.81,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened while you were suspended?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:27.31,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, is this a death sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:29.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to die tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I die!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:33.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you two knock it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:35.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you for listening!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:37.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Remember...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:40.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once those painful exams are\Nover, it'll finally be Christmas.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:44.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, I have an announcement\Nfrom the student council.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:50.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After the last assembly on Christmas Eve,\Nthere will be a voluntary party in the gym.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:51.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Couples are naturally welcome to attend.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:53.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if you're having difficulty in love,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:56.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}or finding it hard to approach\Nthat special someone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.65,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...why not take this opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:11:02.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- A Christmas...\N- Party...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:11:02.18,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to invite them\Nto a romantic Christmas Eve extravaganza?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:05.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear that, Ryuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:06.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:09.81,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to invite Minorin to\Nthat Christmas Eve party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:10.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:13.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that! Tell her\Nstraight up how you feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:14.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,T-T-Tell her how I feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:17.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I couldn't possibly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You should.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:24.24,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's Christmas Eve—the holy night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:28.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And lovely angel Taiga\Nis a messenger of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:30.71,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A child sent from Heaven on Christmas!\NThe ideal obedient child!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:31.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Santa's watching me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:38.88,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll play Cupid to make\Nsure your love is fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:40.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:41.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:43.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh—? H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:44.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:47.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't I look like Cupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:51.27,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, like I said before...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:53.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:58.69,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot Guys Only
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:58.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:03.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The exclusive Christmas party\Nfor hot guys is through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:08.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:10.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh! Look, Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:12.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy's a real cutie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:16.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm perfectly fine with \Nthe intellectual type!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:18.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Heya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful gentleman!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:21.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be a long party!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:24.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not munch on this to keep you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.89,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:28.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I not any fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:34.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I waited so we could entertain each\Nother, it being Christmas and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:35.35,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:37.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Entertain each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:38.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Naked!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:39.82,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We're naked!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:40.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:45.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking for a cuter,\Nsexier, pretty Santa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:47.28,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:49.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,talking about me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:51.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how my dream went.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sick perv. Gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Haruta-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:58.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I get screwed over the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:13:01.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we should talk about the real party.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:03.51,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to select a committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:05.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, Tiger?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep saying how much\Nyou love Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:12.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-If you're all going to nominate\Nme, I-I'm willing to take the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:16.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're joining me, sugar-slug-dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:18.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of dog is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:20.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin, join in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:22.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:23.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:26.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:31.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually not in the mood\Nfor a Christmas party.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:34.08,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to be merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:36.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:40.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I made an unbelievable softball error.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:43.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It basically cost us the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:45.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:52.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If I attend a party after that, I'd lose\Nthe respect of my teammates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:55.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And we have another game after\NNew Year's, so I need to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:57.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:58.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:02.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can still come to the party, even\Nif you don't have time to be on—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:03.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:08.32,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, fine. I'll join in her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:10.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Then count me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:13.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't a party sound fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:16.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use the power of 2-C to fire things up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:21.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:25.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make this clear, Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:28.38,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in your best interest to be nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:29.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:33.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I specialize in planning these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The success of this party,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:37.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,and the odds of bringing a certain someone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:40.27,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,out of her gloomy shell, lie solely with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:46.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You decided you want to join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:49.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:51.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I already said that I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:53.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:55.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up, Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:15:00.42,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:02.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,With Taiga-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:03.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to study for finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:08.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,At the usual restaurant with\NKitamura and the gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:10.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a salmon steak in the frying pan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Heat it up before you eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:13.89,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:16.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be totes lonely, yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:20.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did you just say "totes"? And "yo"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:22.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:24.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a new fad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:26.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the newcomers at work told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:30.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Dis is how people talk now, yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Cray-cray cute, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:36.24,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm like super-duper smart, yo-yo.\N- Yeah, let's stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:37.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're totally butchering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:40.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Dis isn't wrong, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:42.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Dis is so totes awesome, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:45.38,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Inko-chan, look after Yasuko for me.\N- The super-duper bestest way, yo-ya-yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:48.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one I can count on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:54.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Impossible! Im-Impossible!\N- Sh-She's turning on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:55.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Inko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:59.81,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your sweet\Nand lovely nature?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:01.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:04.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the book you borrowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:08.19,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Christmas Menu\NHomemade Chicken Dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Inko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That was very insensitive of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:13.32,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never roast poultry in this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:14.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:16.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:17.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Never?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:21.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Never, ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:25.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:29.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Did you bring them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:30.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:31.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Got 'em right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:34.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The prize for winning\Nthe Mr. Lucky Man contest,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:36.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,also known as The Boss's notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:39.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll make studying for exams way easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:46.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But technically, these also\Nbelong to Kushieda...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.32,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We won together, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:55.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she can't study with us because\Nof work, so it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:58.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop dwelling on the past like an old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:16:59.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't dwelling on the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:01.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Then start walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:05.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We're studying where Minorin's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:09.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to talk with her \Nbefore the others arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:12.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:15.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda took the night off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:19.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Please use the button to call me\Nwhen you're ready to order.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:21.81,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:24.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Minorin avoiding you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:25.89,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why would she!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:28.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You barely talk at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:30.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was the one who invited\Nher to study with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:33.24,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you told me to let you handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:36.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So, have the two of you even talked lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:38.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:40.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She was obviously lying about\Nhaving work tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:43.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,and she won't be coming to\Nthe Christmas Eve party.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:46.83,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because she's feeling down\Nabout making a mistake in a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:50.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And isn't this where {\i1}you're{\i0}\Nsupposed to come in!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:51.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:54.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:57.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure how I'm supposed to help now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:01.31,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Minorin have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:03.81,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you used to be more...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:06.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Takasu and Tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:08.35,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:09.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.98,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:11.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:14.32,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really cold today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:14.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all about down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:17.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Down coats are the best\Nfor keeping you warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:18.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You should buy one, Maruo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:20.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kihara?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:22.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,This is unusual. Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted a copy of The Boss's notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:27.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I don't feel like studying by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:29.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:30.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:31.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take this table.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:32.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:32.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:35.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruta sits on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:36.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:39.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kihara goes next to Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:39.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:40.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:42.35,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And I sit next to Haruta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:43.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:45.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What? H-Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:47.31,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to sit over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:51.81,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:53.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls should sit together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:54.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Tiger?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:55.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:18:59.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to sit next to Taka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:00.95,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:01.82,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:03.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's order.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:04.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's okay with the drink buffet, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:08.08,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but there's no point in\Nmaking everyone get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:09.54,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get our drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:12.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh, I want something hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:15.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiger, help him grab the drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:19.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is chilly today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:22.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:24.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:26.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:29.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you throwing Taiga\Nand Kitamura at each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:31.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Jig's up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:32.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:34.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We want you to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:40.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Kitamura and Tiger\Nmake a good match.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:41.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:44.95,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And you know how Kitamura's heartbroken\Nafter The Boss shot him down?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:48.45,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think a new love\Nwould be the cure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:50.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:53.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiger seems to have a thing for Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:55.25,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's got it bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:59.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing you, you probably didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:01.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're surprised, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:02.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I was all, whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:07.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially when you're the one who's been\Nclosest to Tiger and looking after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:10.89,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, yep. Only natural to be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:12.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:14.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:15.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:18.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:21.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:23.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:25.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:27.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really excited about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.45,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at how beautiful it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:32.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Taiga is in love with Kitamura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:36.88,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I've known that the entire time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:39.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:41.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why am I...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:45.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey, Takasu-kun!\N- {\i1}I don't get it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:47.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:49.31,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel about this, Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:55.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the tiger and Maruo\Nshould be a couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:20:58.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:01.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A little sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:03.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!? Don't you think!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:05.99,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And no matter what they\Nsay, it's not true, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:07.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:08.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:12.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want the tiger and\NMaruo to date, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:18.54,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,They all say it's just 'cuz you're nice\Nand like to take care of others...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:22.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But the truth is that you love Tiger, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:26.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm rooting for you! For real!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:30.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in love with Kitamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:32.81,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kihara!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:34.81,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:36.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:37.90,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:40.32,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:41.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:42.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:45.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:55.00,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohashi Shopping District
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:55.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand confusion, Guns N' Roses, yo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:11.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,In those sleepless nights,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:11.72,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,nemurenai yoruni wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:14.98,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I lay there sighing all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:14.98,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,hitoride tameiki
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:18.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What about everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:18.60,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,minna wa dounano
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:22.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It just feels so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:22.36,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,nandaka samishii
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:28.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A tiny little seed in this huge Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:28.86,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,hiroi daichini hitotsubu no tane
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.57,0:22:32.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Stretch out those roots,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.57,0:22:32.12,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,nekko nobashite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.12,0:22:39.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,and bear a fruit that's still unripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.12,0:22:39.75,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,mada aoi miwo tsuketa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:44.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The fruit that wants to \Nhurry and turn orange.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:44.63,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,orenji ironi hayaku naritai kajitsu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.63,0:22:47.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Showering in your light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.63,0:22:47.84,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kimino hikari wo abite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.84,0:22:51.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,only nurtures bigger ideals and dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.84,0:22:51.47,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,risou ya yume wa fukuramu bakari
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:22:54.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:22:54.85,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kizuiteyo nee
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:23:01.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I ate the orange today but cried\Nbecause it was still too sour.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:23:01.69,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,orenji kyoumo tabete mitakedo\Nmada suppakute naita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.81,0:23:05.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It reminded too much of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.81,0:23:05.19,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,watashi mitaide nokosenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:07.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,so I finished the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:07.61,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,zenbu tabeta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:14.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you. It makes me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:14.16,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,sukidayo nakeruyo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:21.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:21.04,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,sukidayo sukidayo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:35.01,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Underneath the Fir Tree
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:26.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it'll be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.96,0:23:28.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll cheer you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.13,0:23:30.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So you have to come\Nto the party, Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:32.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't undo what I've done...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:34.35,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely... Probably...
